{"tid":1414853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"需要軍事演習","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:06.000Z","uid":282064,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95b3e2966e2278d63dfa056c8bf7e0f09db34a15","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"發夢玩緊Total war<br />\n<br />\n敵軍有騎兵衝黎<br />\n就算前排唔怕 但後排好多人唔識點做 見到敵軍衝過黎 士氣即時大跌只係識跑<br />\n即使係前排係精銳步兵一旦孤立無援都唔會夠騎兵打<br />\n<br />\n所以反正有時和平未開戰真係無咩野做只係係度合唱deus vult個陣<br />\n要搵D機會好似學校呀公司呀做火警演習咁樣 要做返一兩次軍事演習 去train一train應對<br />\n<br />\n冷兵器史上 騎兵大多只可以蹂躪非專業民兵<br />\n如果步兵經過訓練 面對騎兵衝鋒時能夠承受壓力同恐懼<br />\n唔會自亂陣腳 打亂陣型 就算只是單純的盾牆 都有一定的抵擋作用<br />\n當然唔係事必要硬打 單單係有隊型咁撤退 而達至最少損失 都需要訓練<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係敵軍騎兵就算經過專業訓練<br />\n但動物就係動物 天性係無得改<br />\n只要我方陣型不潰散 衝到埋黎都一樣會有壓力同恐懼<br />\n隨時會為自保而剎停 咁我地就有勝機<br />\n<br />\n當然我都明依家以游擊戰術為主 但訓練係唔會嫌多"},{"pid":"ef6fa25f2d473a6f2172d31ccf00e5f725cc9713","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係遊戲台先係呀"},{"pid":"69765ae9fec3f1364c211c472c4e68c69e9d5038","tid":1414853,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"點樣訓練但又唔會俾人見到?"},{"pid":"03c92ee9328f599702cfddfab2c535a37ed3237b","tid":1414853,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e92f7a85353e6c55cfdd6b3b72e322a779d387e7","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69765ae9fec3f1364c211c472c4e68c69e9d5038","tid":1414853,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"點樣訓練但又唔會俾人見到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"見到都唔緊要<br />\n比人知我地有train<br />\n佢地出手前都會有顧忌<br />\n攻城為下 攻心為上"},{"pid":"fd8cb864c3f30f77794beeb55eea1b65015cc6d1","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec94a90068b4eebd659560780bdfca0c56259606","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbf6664dc4c6d32a3f61a97b3213882b63130813","tid":1414853,"uid":41327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"同埋豬嘴呢d基本嘢真係要有，見前線後少少有人得口罩眼罩，食少少就要人抬走。"},{"pid":"7290f62e5066b5cc65e54da84a1d6990ed3891c0","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbf6664dc4c6d32a3f61a97b3213882b63130813","tid":1414853,"uid":41327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"同埋豬嘴呢d基本嘢真係要有，見前線後少少有人得口罩眼罩，食少少就要人抬走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"eed848a17b7c18a655a8c1ac32ac3ff1e55bab24","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b9ed78fac0bcb72ee3042d44224780e38366f82","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"070ee922fa743101f0e7c2f75f3cafafe02550e8","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d9fcf5afcb0d948f2a67fc2282b68b83e04dab","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caa6728e520a0c8f091ad00d362e89e701d07c10","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"052bb9a2bd1b2c4cadb525ebf8d5e7a8c5b15e2a","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3717a492992c6a734b1e2d451576dd4c44f080e","tid":1414853,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:4